== Chemistry == In an estimate by Baruch Shalev, between 1901 and 2000, about 72.5% of [[Nobel Prize in Chemistry|Chemistry Nobel prize]] winners were either [[Christians]] or had a Christian background.<ref name="Nobel Prize" />
